sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS (rustls)
    participant Health as Health Server<br/>8034/TCP HTTP
    participant GenTGIS as TGIS<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    participant GenNLP as caikit-nlp<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    participant GenOAI as OpenAI Server (vLLM)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Chunker as Chunker Service<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    participant Detector as Detector Service(s)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over Client,Detector: Flow 1: Unary Classification with Text Generation (v1)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v1/task/classification-with-text-generation<br/>Headers: passthrough (X-Forwarded-Access-Token)
    Orch->>GenTGIS: gRPC Generate/Tokenize<br/>Optional mTLS
    GenTGIS-->>Orch: Generated text
    Orch->>Chunker: gRPC ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>Optional mTLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text segments
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Optional TLS
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: JSON response with generation + detections

    Note over Client,Detector: Flow 2: OpenAI Chat Completions with Detection (v2)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Headers: passthrough
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/chat (input detection)<br/>Optional TLS
    Detector-->>Orch: Input detection results
    Orch->>GenOAI: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Optional TLS + Bearer token
    GenOAI-->>Orch: Chat completion response (or SSE stream)
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (output detection)<br/>Optional TLS
    Detector-->>Orch: Output detection results
    Orch-->>Client: JSON or SSE stream with detections

    Note over Client,Detector: Flow 3: Streaming Content Detection (v2)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/stream-content<br/>ND-JSON stream input
    Orch->>Chunker: gRPC BidiStreamingChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>Optional mTLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked segments (streaming)
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Optional TLS
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: ND-JSON stream response

    Note over Health: Health & Monitoring
    Client->>Health: GET /health (8034/TCP, no TLS)
    Health-->>Client: Service name + version
    Client->>Health: GET /info (8034/TCP, no TLS)
    Health->>GenTGIS: health()
    Health->>Detector: GET /health
    Health->>Chunker: health()
    Health-->>Client: Downstream service health status
